<number box="[1316,1344,1572,1596]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="10.0">10</number>
</figureCitation>
A, 
<number box="[1381,1409,1572,1596]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="12.0">12</number>
A, 
<number box="[151,179,1608,1632]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="13.0">13</number>
A). Subgenital plates short, broad, depressed, strongly constricted and close together at base, strongly divergent and broadened distally, with few fine setae (
<figureCitation box="[679,769,1644,1669]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="16.[151,250,1574,1596]" captionTargetBox="[190,1399,205,1542]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[177,1409,193,1552]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 10. The holotype of Decliviassus bipunctatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Style, lateral view; D. Subgenital plates, ventral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Apex of aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253719/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
Figs 
<number box="[741,769,1644,1668]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="10.0">10</number>
</figureCitation>
D, 
<number box="[808,835,1644,1668]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="12.0">12</number>
F, 
<number box="[868,896,1644,1668]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="13.0">13</number>
A). Valve long, subquadrate, broadly fused to pygofer at base, posterior margin truncate(
<figureCitation box="[655,744,1679,1704]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="16.[151,250,1574,1596]" captionTargetBox="[190,1399,205,1542]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[177,1409,193,1552]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 10. The holotype of Decliviassus bipunctatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Style, lateral view; D. Subgenital plates, ventral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Apex of aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253719/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
Figs 
<number box="[715,744,1680,1704]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="10.0">10</number>
</figureCitation>
D, 
<number box="[782,809,1680,1704]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="12.0">12</number>
F, 
<number box="[843,871,1680,1704]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="13.0">13</number>
A). Connective well sclerotized, relatively long, straplike, lateral lobes weakly developed, articulated to anteroventral corner of aedeagal atrium, median anterior lobe extended well ventrad of style (
<figureCitation box="[600,692,1751,1776]" captionStart="FIGURE 10" captionStartId="16.[151,250,1574,1596]" captionTargetBox="[190,1399,205,1542]" captionTargetId="figure@16.[177,1409,193,1552]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURE 10. The holotype of Decliviassus bipunctatus sp. nov. A. Genital capsule, lateral view; B. Aedeagus, lateral view; C. Style, lateral view; D. Subgenital plates, ventral view; E. Ventral process of pygofer side, caudolateral view; F. Apex of aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/253719/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
Figs 
<number box="[664,692,1752,1776]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="10.0">10</number>
</figureCitation>
A, 
<number box="[733,759,1752,1776]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="11.0">11</number>
A, 
<number box="[801,829,1752,1776]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="12.0">12</number>
